title: Jesús Sánchez (boxer)
text: Jesús Sánchez (born 1 March 1953) is a Dominican Republic <a href="boxing">boxer</a>. He competed in the <a href="Boxing%20at%20the%201976%20Summer%20Olympics%20%E2%80%93%20Light%20welterweight">men's light welterweight</a> event at the <a href="1976%20Summer%20Olympics">1976 Summer Olympics</a>.
